# Workforce

### How to use

- Make sure to have [Node.js 20](https://nodejs.org/en/download) installed.
- Run `yarn`.
- Run `yarn start` (this will start the server).
- Navigate to the client directory: `cd client/`.
- Run `yarn`.
- Run `yarn dev` (this will start the client).

### To do next

